strings:
<voice_0x010017CE><se_def>*: Good morning! So today's the day!
You're going to face our Lord, aren't you?

<voice_0x010017CF><se_def>*: I humbly wish you the best of luck.
We can't go on like this.
<voice_0x010017D0><se_low>Chen Mui: If you are injured, or tire on your way to the Heavenly Dais, you should return to my house and rest.
<voice_0x010017D1><se_low>Chen Mui: I've made arrangements so that you can stay whenever you like. Just ask my attendant.
